
As of 0.0.7 the user can change the display mode without quitting slurm.
Just press "m" to cycle between modes or

    - "c" for the old combined/classic mode
    - "s" for the split window mode with stats
    - "l" for the large window mode w/o stats

    - "z" to reset most counters
    - "r" to redraw the screen
    - "q" to quit slurm

